<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="id">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Login | PT Digital Nusantara</title>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Plus+Jakarta+Sans:wght@400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@tabler/icons-webfont@2.45.0/tabler-icons.min.css">
  <style>
    * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
    body { font-family: 'Plus Jakarta Sans', sans-serif; background: #f5f3f0; min-height: 100vh; }
    .login-wrapper {
      min-height: 100vh;
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    }
    .login-left {
      background: #1a1a1a;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      justify-content: center;
      padding: 60px;
      color: #fff;
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
    }
    .login-left::after {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      bottom: -80px;
      right: -80px;
      width: 300px;
      height: 300px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.03);
    }
    .login-left h1 {
      font-size: 32px;
      font-weight: 700;
      margin-bottom: 12px;
      line-height: 1.2;
    }
    .login-left p {
      color: #999;
      font-size: 15px;
      line-height: 1.6;
      max-width: 360px;
    }
    .login-left .brand-badge {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 10px;
      margin-bottom: 40px;
      padding: 8px 14px;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
      border-radius: 8px;
      font-size: 13px;
      color: #ccc;
    }
    .login-left .brand-badge i { font-size: 20px; color: #7c9a92; }
    .login-right {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      padding: 40px;
    }
    .login-form {
      width: 100%;
      max-width: 380px;
    }
    .login-form h2 {
      font-size: 24px;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: #1a1a1a;
      margin-bottom: 6px;
    }
    .login-form .subtitle {
      color: #777;
      font-size: 14px;
      margin-bottom: 32px;
    }
    .form-group { margin-bottom: 20px; }
    .form-group label {
      display: block;
      font-size: 13px;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: #444;
      margin-bottom: 6px;
    }
    .form-group input, .form-group select {
      width: 100%;
      padding: 11px 14px;
      border: 1px solid #ddd;
      border-radius: 8px;
      font-size: 14px;
      font-family: inherit;
      background: #fff;
      transition: border-color 0.2s;
    }
    .form-group input:focus {
      outline: none;
      border-color: #7c9a92;
      box-shadow: 0 0 0 3px rgba(124,154,146,0.1);
    }
    .captcha-section {
      background: #fafaf8;
      border: 1px solid #e8e6e3;
      border-radius: 10px;
      padding: 16px;
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    .captcha-section .question {
      font-size: 20px;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: #333;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }
    .captcha-section input {
      width: 120px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 18px;
      font-weight: 600;
      padding: 8px 12px;
      border: 1px solid #ddd;
      border-radius: 8px;
      font-family: inherit;
    }
    .captcha-section input:focus {
      outline: none;
      border-color: #7c9a92;
    }
    .remember-row {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
      margin-bottom: 24px;
      font-size: 13px;
    }
    .remember-row label { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 6px; color: #555; cursor: pointer; }
    .remember-row a { color: #7c9a92; text-decoration: none; font-weight: 500; }
    .remember-row a:hover { text-decoration: underline; }
    .btn-login {
      width: 100%;
      padding: 12px;
      background: #1a1a1a;
      color: #fff;
      border: none;
      border-radius: 8px;
      font-size: 14px;
      font-weight: 600;
      font-family: inherit;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: background 0.2s;
    }
    .btn-login:hover { background: #333; }
    .alert {
      padding: 12px 14px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      font-size: 13px;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      font-weight: 500;
    }
    .alert-danger { background: #fef2f2; color: #b91c1c; border: 1px solid #fecaca; }
    .alert-success { background: #f0fdf4; color: #166534; border: 1px solid #bbf7d0; }
    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      .login-wrapper { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .login-left { display: none; }
      .login-right { padding: 24px; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="login-wrapper">
  <div class="login-left">
    <div class="brand-badge">
      <i class="ti ti-building"></i>
      PT Digital Nusantara
    </div>
    <h1>Kelola karyawan<br>dengan mudah.</h1>
    <p>Sistem manajemen karyawan yang membantu Anda mengelola data, divisi, dan laporan dalam satu tempat.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="login-right">
    <div class="login-form">
      <h2>Masuk</h2>
      <p class="subtitle">Silakan masuk ke akun Anda</p>

      <% if (locals.error) { %><div class="alert alert-danger"><%= error %></div><% } %>
      <% if (locals.success) { %><div class="alert alert-success"><%= success %></div><% } %>

      <form method="POST" action="/auth/login">
        <div class="form-group">
          <label>Username</label>
          <input type="text" name="username" required autofocus placeholder="Masukkan username">
        </div>
        <div class="form-group">
          <label>Password</label>
          <input type="password" name="password" required placeholder="Masukkan password">
        </div>
        <div class="captcha-section">
          <div class="question"><%= captcha.question %></div>
          <input type="number" name="captcha" required placeholder="?">
        </div>
        <div class="remember-row">
          <label><input type="checkbox" name="remember"> Ingat saya</label>
          <a href="/auth/forgot-password">Lupa password?</a>
        </div>
        <button type="submit" class="btn-login">Masuk</button>
      </form>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
</body>
</html>
